Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:39.72,biaoti2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,285)}世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来中杉小夜香被硫加寄生的事实是错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通过你得到的样本的分析结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确认了硫加的存在数据
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麦基乌斯警官  真的没有拯救宿主的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  你的心情可以理解  但恐怕已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗官到达地球就会马上开始对硫加的处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一旦开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不会在乎给地球造成多大伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在乎地球的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  到太空船上来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好  有件事必须告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警官！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君  你身体的修复工作完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  巴迪  你不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然高兴了  太好了  功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦  自由真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了嘛  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易我们都恢复到原来的身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  其实  硫加…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学就是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  骗人啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我不管什么事情都能以豁达的胸襟接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新学期刚开始就一副松懈的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀  是早宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  约会进展怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不至于袭击了中杉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你别瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉来了我可得问问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你慌什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…早宫！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是中杉同学的爷爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs20\fad(0,1200)}中杉IT公司的会长被杀\N于家中工作的佣人铃木良枝（64）\N因涉嫌杀人正在被追查之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  开学典礼马上开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要早退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前中杉家这边如画面所示已经进行了交通管制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现场陷于混乱的气氛中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前还没有抓到犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将关注警方今后的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  让我过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  这里不让过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  中杉小夜香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  说你呢  不许进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您拨打的电话可能不在服务区内或者正关机  暂时无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉的爷爷看着那么慈祥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事件当天开始下落不明的中杉家的佣人作为重要嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佣人指的是铃木良枝？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只是在中杉同学的身边不断发生奇怪的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是被卷进了什么麻烦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  其实呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始能暂时留在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果她遇到什么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  希望你能帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  巴迪  事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和中杉同学联络上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能  她家里的电话也没人接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情况还很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媒体也有很多人在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川君今天真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是个懒虫  不用管他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经第三天了  到极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  再待一会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  硫加那方面没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…调查还很费劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  但要是知道了什么消息就跟我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我帮不上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不快点找到硫加就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  巴迪也没精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  抓到硫加了怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,处理…啊  就是杀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  被硫加寄生的人会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会一起死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉胜利遇害事件的调查情况没有什么进展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉工业技术公司正在举行葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏玛朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功…功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你满意了吧  到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  再等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在和中杉取得联系前我想就这样守望着她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  功  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须和你说点事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实硫加的事情已经查清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加就寄生在中杉同学身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要把中杉同学给…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功？唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  关键时刻你竟然睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  要赶紧回到中杉同学那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后捕获她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要说的话不是「捕获」而是「保护」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆把她藏家里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉小姐被硫加寄生了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加在她体内成长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她自身正逐渐变成硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要捕获她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开这么无聊的玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我怎么相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她的汗水成分中查到了硫加的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她的汗水是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你利用了我是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  但硫加对地球来说太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去全人类都会灭亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把中杉同学杀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不把硫加处理掉会死很多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是中杉同学…中杉同学她又没做错什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么一定要杀她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,理解一下  功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了拯救众多的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是弄错了  说她是硫加一定是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身体怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我决不让你到中杉同学那儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川功封住了巴迪的意识  控制了身体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经出现精神融合的征兆了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才真是危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麦基乌斯警官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我要求她全面协助神祗厅  可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  按她说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有保护千川功生活的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没那个必要了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？咦？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该通知了你会把他的身体带来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不能擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没时间争论这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要马上捕获硫加并处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服  衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜  眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀  偏偏这时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了  请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是从这里消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能估计到她会去哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起到处瞎找不如在这等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你不愿捕获硫加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗厅真的不知道解救被硫加寄生的宿主的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  没那样的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我想说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是联邦搜查官吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像还有个其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能还是快点控制住硫加比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方会自己送上门来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的做法不会有失误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  突然来访
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手机放在亲戚的婆婆那里了  没法和你联系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事  中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很不安  很孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷竟然去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连良枝阿姨都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…放哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  看到千川同学的脸就松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有很多人在家里进出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不太友善的那种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  大家都很亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都是刚见面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很亲切  亲切到让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功吗  中杉同学跟你在一块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  她不在我这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想强行带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把中杉同学交给我  功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加要被处理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学已经和硫加同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,硫加显现出来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上又会重复比尔盖巴的惨剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人类会全部灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她才不是硫加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来说服失败了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祗厅对硫加的处理延期了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦政府内部在对硫加的处理一事上产生了争议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有人想拿地球来做硫加的试验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「失落技术」的试验场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,低度文明的当地人死多少都无所谓的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们逃跑吧  中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢现在聚在你身边的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能去他们那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我远走高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离这里远远的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学  来  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点逃亡者的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到哪里去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去北方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是去南方？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的尽头怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没带护照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说认真的啊  千川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:17:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一边抢银行  一边亡命天涯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用担心钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来练习下逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就像「雌雄大盗」那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(369,363)\fs23}Bonnie and Clyde
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的一部电影  讲的是一对恋人一边抢银行一边旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…那两人最后怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被警官开枪击中  两人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川同学跟我一块的话死也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能立马回答就没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没关系  我会当盾牌守护千川同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能那样  我好歹也是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护中杉同学而死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  千川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去萨塔吉特·夏玛朗先生那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏玛朗？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,远房亲戚都只是想要爷爷的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷公司里的也是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是夏玛朗先生很尊重爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很担心公司和我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人一起逃到哪里去  太孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护中杉同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去夏玛朗先生那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点急  但心理顾问说这时候快点行动会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乘船旅行能换换心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时到外国生活也是不错的经历
